 MBOMBELA – On Tuesday morning motorists were greeted with an unusual scene next to the side of the road on their way to work. Umbali Wedding and Function venue held a mock-wedding next to the R40 across the road from Sonpark on the grass in front of Town Lodge. “We want to showcase that weddings can still be fun as well as create awareness of our open day on Sunday,” said Umbali owner Theresa Schoeman. The open day will feature a variety of wedding vendors ranging from dresses and cakes to decor and photographers. ALSO READ: The 10 best wedding songs of 2018 Even though the bride and groom met each other only moments before the ceremony, it was great fun and an extraordinary siting next to the road.  ALSO WATCH: 10 hilarious royal wedding memes that will make you smile